;==============================================================================
; WORDLE WORD LIST - In-Order (Alphabetical) - 2,315 words
;==============================================================================
; Words stored in alphabetical order (in-order BST traversal).
; Standard binary search works perfectly on this array.
;
; Search algorithm:
;   start = 0, end = 2314
;   while start <= end:
;     mid = (start + end) / 2
;     compare search_word with words[mid]
;     if equal: FOUND!
;     if less: end = mid - 1
;     if greater: start = mid + 1
;==============================================================================

